                    <span>I'm an experienced seminar leader (I've trained over 30,000 people in my career) and still got plenty of great tips from Fred's superb resource.    Handling difficult people, how to sell better from the podium, as well as a lot of new tips that will help me do even better.  Thanks Fred - nice work!   Get this book if you do seminars.</span>
                  
              
